OSQLFunction
public class OSQLFunctionUnionAll extends OSQLFunctionMultiValueAbstract<Collection<Object>>
This operator can work as aggregate or inline. If only one argument is passed than aggregates, otherwise executes, and returns, a UNION of the collections received as parameters. Works also with no collection values. Does not remove duplication from the result.
Author:
Luca Garulli (l.garulli--(at)--orientdb.com)
